Capitau Talks to Tax Body to Revive Avusa Bid, Bus. Report Says

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-09-30T04:58:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/capitau-talks-to-tax-body-to-revive-avusa-bid-bus-report-says.html
Capitau Holdings Ltd. is in talks
with the South African Revenue Service to try and win approval
for a bid for  Avusa Ltd. (AVU) , Johannesburg’s Business Report said,
citing David Fields, Capitau’s chief executive officer.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
